{
  "info": {
    "name": "Hify · Provider 模型供应商管理（第1轮）",
    "description": "Admin 模型供应商 CRUD + 启用/禁用 的接口测试集。\n\n用法：\n1. 先跑「0. 登录(admin)」拿 token（自动存入集合变量 token，后续请求自动带 Bearer）。\n2. 跑「2. 创建-OpenAI兼容」会把返回 id 存入 providerId，供更新/启停/删除复用。\n3. 集合变量里改 baseUrl / adminUsername / adminPassword 适配你的环境。\n\n约定：所有响应是 Result 信封 {code,message,data,traceId}；成功 code=200；id 为字符串；apiKey 明文/密文绝不出响应（只回 apiKeyTail 后4位）。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminUsername",
      "value": "admin"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminPassword",
      "value": "change-me-on-first-deploy"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "providerId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "anthropicProviderId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "modelId",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. 登录(admin) → 存 token",
      "request": {
        "auth": {
          "type": "noauth"
        },
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/identity/login",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "v1",
            "identity",
            "login"
          ]
        },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{adminUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('登录成功 code=200', () => pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(200));",
              "pm.test('返回 token', () => pm.expect(json.data.token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty);",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. 列表",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/provider/providers",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "v1",
            "admin",
            "provider",
            "providers"
          ]
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(200));",
              "pm.test('data 是数组', () => pm.expect(json.data).to.be.an('array'));",
              "if (json.data.length) {",
              "  pm.test('id 为字符串', () => pm.expect(json.data[0].id).to.be.a('string'));",
              "  pm.test('不泄露密文/明文 key', () => { pm.expect(json.data[0]).to.not.have.property('apiKeyCipher'); pm.expect(json.data[0]).to.not.have.property('apiKey'); });",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. 创建-OpenAI兼容 → 存 providerId",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/provider/providers",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "v1",
            "admin",
            "provider",
            "providers"
          ]
        },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"通义千问-生产\",\n  \"protocol\": \"openai\",\n  \"baseUrl\": \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1\",\n  \"apiKey\": \"sk-test-openai-1234abcd\"\n}"
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(200));",
              "pm.test('protocol=openai', () => pm.expect(json.data.protocol).to.eql('openai'));",
              "pm.test('掩码尾巴=abcd', () => pm.expect(json.data.apiKeyTail).to.eql('abcd'));",
              "pm.test('状态默认 enabled', () => pm.expect(json.data.status).to.eql('enabled'));",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('providerId', json.data.id);"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
